the execution is aborted.

\S{varrccount} RCCOUNT - RC buffer execution command count

Doubleword.
This is reset to zero when RC buffer execution starts.
Each time a command is executed from the RC buffer,
this variable is incremented.
If it reaches the value of RCLIMIT,
RC buffer execution is aborted.


